org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface ITypedExpressionNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IExpressionNode, IIdentifierNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TypedExpressionNode

    public interface ITypedExpressionNode
extends IIdentifierNode
    An AST node representing a parameterized type such as Vector.<Sprite>.

    The shape of this node is: 

     ITypedExpressionNode
   IExpressionNode <-- getTypeNode()
   IExpressionNode <-- getCollectionNode()
    For example, 
    Vector.<Sprite>
    is represented as 
     ITypedExpressionNode
   IIdentifierNode "Vector"
   IIdentifierNode "Sprite"
